commentTextItems.html: That's it. India level the series. Kartik seals the victory with a crisp straight drive. Low full toss and down came the bat, met the ball flush in the middle and it raced past the bowler, past the diving mid-on and into the advertising hoards. Handshakes all around. On the field and in the Indian dressing room.

commentPostTextItems.html: India were wobbling a touch at 94 for 4 on this two-paced track but Rahul Dravid and Mahendra Singh Dhoni stitched together 133 runs to steer India home. Goa is place to party and it will the hosts who will be enjoying the dinner on or near some lovely beach tonight.

"Touch wood. Things have been good for me. County cricket has helped. Physio is taking good care of me and maintaining my rhythm."  Zaheer shakes hand with the sponsors, sits on top of the prize bike to pose for the cameras.

We shall leave Zaheer with his new toy and take your leave. This is Sriram Veera, along with Jamie Alter, signing off.  But don't go anywhere. Please join George Binoy for the last ODI between South Africa and Pakistan. SA lead 2-1.
